1. http (http 기준)
    - post
    - put
    - get
    - delete
2. db (query 기준)
    - insert
    - update
    - find
    - delete
3. file (shared preference 기준)
    - put
    - put 공통
    - get
    - remove
4. repository
    - save
    - update
    - get
    - delete
5. class
    - {description}{component}
    - ex) WriteFragment / NotificationService ..
6. layout
    - {component}{description}
    - ex) fragment_write / activity_modify / {bottom_sheet}_{person_preview}
7. drawable
    - {what}_{where}_{description}_{size} : 순서만 이대로 중간중간 없어도됨
    - 아이콘의 ic 는 필수로 들어가는게 좋을듯
    - where/description 은 무조건 필수 (where 공통은 common)
    - ex) {ic}_{common}_{back_arrow} / {common}_{btn_red}_{small}
            {splash}_{background}
8. color/string
    - {where}_{description}
    - ex) {splash}_{title} = "타이틀" / {common}_{big_button} = "#ffffffff"